    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178280/extras/a96301723c7d62f632711f4c10ab3e7b.poster.avif?t=1667506116\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178280/extras/a96301723c7d62f632711f4c10ab3e7b.webm?t=1667506116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178280/extras/a96301723c7d62f632711f4c10ab3e7b.mp4?t=1667506116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Welcome to Penguinland Glacier! Join aboard the Pengreens™ Team!<br>Here we deliver eletrical supplies along all the Glacier!<br><br>Hop on and let's start to work!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178280/extras/c2bb7266aa1925e89559fb067a1a6c7f.poster.avif?t=1667506116\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178280/extras/c2bb7266aa1925e89559fb067a1a6c7f.webm?t=1667506116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178280/extras/c2bb7266aa1925e89559fb067a1a6c7f.mp4?t=1667506116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Travel along the glacier loading batteries and solar panels into delivery trucks, but be careful during your tasks!<br>Solar panels are fragile and will break if you jump from too high with them! Batteries are more resistant, but heavier and will limit your jump abilities.<br><br>Move between corridors of ice procedualy generated in each level, and avoid to break Carbon Crates to ensure energetic efficiency every level.<br>Unlock every Carbon Credit possible on Penguinland Glacier by repairing all the Energy Windmills and finishing your deliveries within the time limit!<br><br>Achieve a environment balanced Penguinland and restore it to its glory!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178280/extras/4d471c5dedc72b1a96084e3851796c95.poster.avif?t=1667506116\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178280/extras/4d471c5dedc72b1a96084e3851796c95.webm?t=1667506116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178280/extras/4d471c5dedc72b1a96084e3851796c95.mp4?t=1667506116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play along 25 levels crafted to use the most out of the block stacking mechanics.<br>Chalenge yourself against the clock to get more credits on every level.<br>Complete aditional chalenges in some levels to get more Carbon Credits.<br>Be the change that will make Penguinland thrive!",
